params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_CD as CS_PROC_CD, " +" M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_NAME as CS_PROC_NAME, " +" M_CS_PROC.WS_CD as WS_CD, " +" M_WS.WS_NAME as WS_NAME, " +" M_CS_PROC.OUTSIDE_TYP as OUTSIDE_TYP_DN, " +" M_CS_PROC.VEND_CD as VEND_CD, " +" M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_ANAME as VEND_ANAME, " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.MODIFY_COUNT) as MODIFY_COUNT " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_WS, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD(+) = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.VEND_CD " +" and M_WS.WS_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.WS_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.CTRL_CD(+) = 'SYSTEM' " +" and M_CS_PROC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_CD like ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.WS_CD like ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.DEL_FLG = to_number(?) " +"order by " +" M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_CD"

"select " +" M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_CD as CS_PROC_CD, " +" M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_NAME as CS_PROC_NAME, " +" M_CS_PROC.WS_CD as WS_CD, " +" M_WS.WS_NAME as WS_NAME, " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.OUTSIDE_TYP) as OUTSIDE_TYP, " +" M_CS_PROC.VEND_CD as VEND_CD, " +" M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_NAME as VEND_NAME, " +" M_CS_PROC.COMPANY_CD as COMPANY_CD, " +" M_CS_PROC.ORG_CD as ORG_CD, " +" M_ORG.ORG_NAME as ORG_NAME, " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.STD_COST_OF_MONTH) as STD_COST_OF_MONTH, " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.STD_COST_UNIT_TYP) as STD_COST_UNIT_TYP, " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.MODIFY_COUNT) as MODIFY_COUNT " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_ORG " +"where " +" M_WS.WS_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.WS_CD " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.COMPANY_CD " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.VEND_CD " +" and M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.COMPANY_CD " +" and M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.ORG_CD " +" and M_CS_PROC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_CD = ?"

"select " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC " +"where " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"
"select " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC " +"where " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" M_CS_PROC " +"set " +" \\"RCY_TYP_CD\\" = '*', " +" \\"CS_PROC_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"WS_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"VEND_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ORG_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"STD_COST_OF_MONTH\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"STD_COST_UNIT_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"UPDATE_TYP\\" = 2, " +" \\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0 " +"where " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_NAME\\" as \\"ORG_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ORG " +"where " +" M_ORG.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ORG.\\"ORG_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_CS_PUCH.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_CS_PUCH " +"where " +" M_CS_PUCH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PUCH.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PUCH.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0"

"select " +" M_PROC_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0"

"select " +" COUNT(1) " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_WS, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD(+) = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.VEND_CD " +" and M_WS.WS_CD(+) = M_CS_PROC.WS_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.CTRL_CD(+) = 'SYSTEM' " +" and M_CS_PROC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.CS_PROC_CD like ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.WS_CD like ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.DEL_FLG = to_number(?) " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1 " +""
